deps:
* git
* rg (https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep)
* vim + vim-plug (https://github.com/junegunn/vim-plug)
* tmux
* asdf, node (for CoC), erlang, rebar3, etc... (see asdf docs)

install
* install deps
* copy bashrc to $HOME/.bashrc
* copy global_gitconfig to $HOME/.gitconfig
* copy vimrc to $HOME/.vimrc
* copy tmux.conf to $HOME/.tmux.conf
* copy coc-settings.json to $HOME/.vim/coc-settings.json
* config terminal font and colors according to term_config file
